title: The Spotlight Effect
itunes:title: The Spotlight Effect
description:
Episode 616 - What you focus on magnifies. We've all heard it before but how do we truly use this wisdom? In this episode, I am going to teach you how to stop focusing on what you don't want and start focusing on what you really want in your life.
